cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO

This paper deals with computer vision and graphics, specifically with the problem of inverse rendering for indoor scenes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves graphics and rendering techniques, which suggests the category cs.GR (Computer Graphics). The use of deep learning and physical insights in the proposed framework indicates the categories cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper mentions applications for augmented reality, which could fall under the category cs.RO (Robotics).
